  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: An initial implementation of \"Advanced Settings\" (AS) was done so now only \"Mailserver\" options are displayed on the right panel. Now that we need to add more items under AS, we need to apply a more \"condensed\" design.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTo be able to see all \"Mailserver\" options under a dropdown, so we can show other options like #5848 also under AS.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nCurrent implementation:\r\n<img width=\"1023\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-17 a la s 5 47 28 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45634299-4b900c80-baa2-11e8-8289-8805cf2dd0b9.png\">\r\n\r\nOriginal design:\r\n<img width=\"736\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-17 a la s 5 49 56 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45634259-31562e80-baa2-11e8-862b-7f66d6536121.png\">\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to \"Profile\"\r\n- Go to \"Advanced Options\"\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n- [ ] Implement mailserver options under a dropdown. See dropdown behavior design here >> zpl.io/a74lJJE (Zeplin)\r\n",
